title: Douglas Adams E-book Library
description:
Libary of ebooks by Douglas Adams in pdf, .lit and word doc format to ensure almost almost anyone may enjoy reading these books

This libaray includes the following books

1. Dirk Gently's Holistic Detective Agency
2. The Long Dark Tea-Time of the Soul
3. The lost chapters
4. Young Zaphod Play's it safe
5. Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy
6. Restaurant at the end of the Universe
7. So long and Thanks for All The Fish
8. Mostly Harmless
9. Starship Titanic
10. The Meaning of Life
11. The Private Life of Gengis Khan
12. The Salmon of Doubt
13. Last Chance to see.

The books have been compressed in .rar format and can be opened using winrar.
